/v/t64.5771-25/227837668_1656549748425991_1143631201984089429_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=nLb7VXLHSSMQ7kNvgHjCMaE&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCnc4eun-BUr2sjCO8wPrDEg9psBJvpCvkySXAaPIAAYg&oe=672B6208"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "4.png", "id": "1838571613315973", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003272_1838571616649306_6242989053745109081_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=NrzbWIFELK0Q7kNvgHirX28&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC61ykvgT0PwxsYPrROFK4x05HjVOz5gKBqeWfbXe68Gw&oe=672B3E5C"}, "display_name": "Testvr", "keywords": [], "long_description": "The VRzomOl is a VRFPS game that focuses on PVP network online biochemical battle mode, an improvement from the original CS's popular biochemical mode. The game features two modes: zombie escape and biochemical infection. In these modes, online players must play as either humans or zombies. Within a limited time frame, humans must either annihilate all zombies or save themselves, while zombies aim to infect all humans through an all-out attack.\n1. Biochemical infection: Within a limited timeframe, humans must eliminate all zombies using firearms or evade them in order to prolong survival, while the zombies actively seek out humans to infect them.\n2. Zombie escape: Within a restricted time frame, humans are required to fend off zombies with firearms for self-preservation and successfully reach the designated endpoint in order to achieve successful escape. The immediate infection of all human players by zombies results in victory.", "short_description": "The first VR Biochemical frenzy online battle in history, Multiplayer shooter in VR with zombies escape, officially opened"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://vrdanceyinsi.webnode.page/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Holoren", "support_website_url": null, "websi